OL,6,FA teenage driver who killed his friend
OL,7,Fin a crash the day after he passed his
OL,8,Ftest has been jailed.
OL,10,FA judge said Corey Cooper was was
OL,11,F"driving a car deplorably, almost
OL,12,Fcertainly trying to show off to
OL,13,Ffriends" when he caused the crash
OL,14,Fwhich killed Josh Atkins.
OL,16,FCooper, who was 17 at the time,
OL,17,Fadmitted causing Josh's death by
OL,18,Fdangerous driving and seriously
OL,19,Finjuring another friend, Gabe Wiggett.
OL,21,FHe was jailed for five years.
