OL,3,CTeen driver who killed friend day
OL,4,Cafter passing test jailed
OL,6,FSheffield Crown Court heard how all
OL,7,Fthree teenagers in the car were 17
OL,8,Fwhen Cooper, now 19, crashed his
OL,9,Fgrandfather's Fiat Grande Punto car in
OL,10,Fthe Stannington area of Sheffield on
OL,11,FNovember 11 2023.
OL,13,FIan West, prosecuting, said police
OL,14,Festimated the car was travelling at
OL,15,Fabout 53mph in a 20mph area of Myers
OL,16,FGrove Lane when the defendant lost
OL,17,Fcontrol on a bend and collided with a
OL,18,Fmetal barrier.
