OL,3,CTeen driver who killed friend day
OL,4,Cafter passing test jailed
OL,6,FMr West said a girl in a car which was
OL,7,Ffollowing said the Fiat "just shot
OL,8,Foff" when it reached a straight
OL,9,Fsection of road, adding: "He went that
OL,10,Ffast we lost sight of him."
OL,12,FHe said the girl described coming
OL,13,Facross the the car on its roof, with
OL,14,Fthe defendant covered in blood,
OL,15,Fstanding by it saying: "What have I
OL,16,Fdone, what have I done, I've killed my
OL,17,Fbest friend."
OL,19,FThe prosecutor described how Cooper
OL,20,Fhad been driving at speed earlier in
OL,21,Fthe evening.
