OL,6,FOne of his friends said they thought
OL,7,Fhe was driving at about 80mph past
OL,8,FBradfield School, in the village of
OL,9,FWorrall.
OL,11,FHe said the defendant was also
OL,12,Fperforming wheel spins in a car park
OL,13,Fin the Lodge Moor area of the city, as
OL,14,Fhe relaxed with friends.
OL,16,FMr West said friends also noted that
OL,17,Fthe Fiat's dashboard warning lights
OL,18,Fwere "lit up like a Christmas tree"
OL,19,Ffor 90 minutes before the crash, and
OL,20,Fthis was because the ABS system was
OL,21,Fnot working properly.
