OL,3,CTeen driver who killed friend day
OL,4,Cafter passing test jailed
OL,6,FThe court heard that Josh died on his
OL,7,Ffather Gavin's birthday.
OL,9,FSentencing Cooper, Judge Jeremy
OL,10,FRichardson KC told him: "This case
OL,11,Fshould be called to the attention of
OL,12,Fall young people who have just passed
OL,13,Fthe driving test.
OL,15,F"It is a case of a young man aged 17,
OL,16,Fas you were, driving a car deplorably,
OL,17,Falmost certainly trying to show off to
OL,18,Ffriends.
