OL,3,CTeen driver who killed friend day
OL,4,Cafter passing test jailed
OL,6,F"In consequence of your driving too
OL,7,Ffast, that young man ` you ` killed a
OL,8,Ffriend and maimed another friend.
OL,10,F"A young life has been ended. Another
OL,11,Ftwo lives have been ruined. For what?
OL,12,FShowing off to friends."
OL,14,FThe judge said it was "truly appalling
OL,15,Fdriving" and Cooper displayed
OL,16,F"immaturity on a grand scale".
OL,18,FHe added: "This case depicts human
OL,19,Ftragedy in every dimension."
OL,21,F'Fight for change'
