OL,3,CTeen driver who killed friend day
OL,4,Cafter passing test jailed
OL,6,FSpeaking outside court, Josh's aunt
OL,7,FClaire Chapman said her nephew's death
OL,8,Fwas "senseless". She described him as
OL,9,F"full of promise, laughter and
OL,10,Fhappiness" and said his organs had
OL,11,Fbeen donated to save four lives.
OL,13,FShe added: "Today marks the end of a
OL,14,Fpainful chapter in our lives, but not
OL,15,Fthe end of our grief, and it is just
OL,16,Fthe beginning of our fight for change."
OL,18,FMs Chapman called for more "education
OL,19,Fand accountability" for young drivers
OL,20,Fbefore they are given "full driving
OL,21,Flicence privileges".
