OL,3,CTeen driver who killed friend day
OL,4,Cafter passing test jailed
OL,6,F"This is not about punishment, it is
OL,7,Fabout prevention," she added.
OL,9,F"Josh was Corey Cooper's best friend.
OL,10,FCorey passed his driving test just the
OL,11,Fday before, his recklessness took Josh
OL,12,Ffrom us.
OL,14,F"If such a system was in place, Josh
OL,15,Fwould still be with us today, still
OL,16,Fliving his life.
OL,18,F"We urge lawmakers to listen. We urge
OL,19,Fother families to join us. Please let
OL,20,FJosh's legacy be more than tragedy.
OL,21,FLet it be the spark that saves others."
